{"tid":1740541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆失守啦！！ 今晚一齊去重建！","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:09.000Z","uid":61886,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"3587e7595803de390cbea630bfe007cf49630759","tid":1740541,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"今晚既然無咩大型活動<br />\n不如一人print幾張文宣<br />\n重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEkrNo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEkrNo1.jpg&h=6757544c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56k7wQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56k7wQH.jpg&h=0e0228e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLO1Bhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLO1Bhn.jpg&h=43841614&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnxqivJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnxqivJ.jpg&h=39d97ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGcNwQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGcNwQK.jpg&h=91b0818a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYjW9Cq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYjW9Cq.jpg&h=60653dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nifWqaM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnifWqaM.jpg&h=ed7f13f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pjPLaN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pjPLaN.jpg&h=90c196c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uB252Xt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuB252Xt.jpg&h=ca1a2cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mu98ghu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMu98ghu.jpg&h=2f3ff968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ff831b79886fd848422f093b607f